metadata.name: Cambium Amour
metadata.description:
she peels away her bark  
to consume my love  
with the tender touch of cambium

I discover her soul  
she goes by heartwood  
in the depths of cambium amour

From "Cambium Amour" Collection by Brendan S Bigney (The Nuclear Cowboy), Marine Corps Veteran, photographer, international speaker and leader, and Multi-Award-Winning Author.
